about Dr. Kaelin

Professional high quality gynecology care for women of all ages

Dr. Kaelin is a consultant gynaecologist, with over 15 years’ experience, who sees female patients between the ages of 16-80 years old who prefer a female doctor. Alongside her private practice at the Portland Hospital, she is a senior consultant in the NHS.

Gynecology care packages

Got any questions?
send an inquiry

Gynecological Ultrasound

450$

A gynecological ultrasound is a safe, non-invasive imaging procedure used to assess the health of the female reproductive organs, including the uterus, ovaries, and fallopian tubes. It helps diagnose conditions such as ovarian cysts, uterine fibroids, pelvic pain, and irregular bleeding.

read more
book now

Gynecological Examination

600$

A gynecological examination is a routine procedure performed by healthcare providers to assess the health of the female reproductive system, including the vulva, vagina, cervix, uterus, and ovaries.

read more
book now

Contraception Consultation

410$

A contraception consultation is a personalized healthcare service designed to help individuals and couples explore safe and effective methods of birth control. During the consultation, a healthcare provider reviews your medical history, lifestyle, and reproductive goals to recommend the most suitable contraceptive options.

read more
book now

Menopausal Symptoms

350$

Menopause marks the end of a woman's reproductive years, typically occurring between ages 45 and 55. It is characterized by a decline in estrogen and other hormone levels, which can lead to a variety of symptoms.
